
#### get all
GET http://localhost:4000/api/categories

### get by id
GET http://localhost:4000/api/categories/78

#### insert record
POST http://localhost:4000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "users": {
    "first_name": "john",
    "last_name": "doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "hashedpwd",
    "phone": "09112312",
    "birth_date": "11/06/2025",
    "address": "asdasdasdsda"
  },
  "users_details": {
    "employment_status": "active",
    "position": "technician"
  }
}

### update record
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "School asds",
  "tagline": "Everything you need for school",
  "id": 91
}

### update record
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/categories/91/disable
